originalText.text: I have been renting out my closet with StyleLend for a few months now.  It’s so easy!  They provide the shipping labels and all you have to do is put it in the mail.  Getting paid is just as easy!  I love the app and the customer support is excellent.   Highly recommend if you are looking for a little extra money.  They have a huge selection of designer products that are very affordable to rent too!

originalText.text:
I have been using Stylelend for the last few years and love it!

This is a great idea - you can rent out your closet and also borrow from the closets of some very fashionable women! It allows me to try out new styles, save money (the rental prices here are cheaper than rent the runway) and earn money. How can you argue with a triple win?

The CEO, Lona Alia, is very responsive and all my experiences have been terrific. I would highly encourage anyone reading this to try out the app.

originalText.text: I cannot say enough amazing things about Style Lend!  I used the amazing wardrobe available via Style Lend to dress myself for my TV show "Million Dollar Matchmaker" this past season.  It was such much more economical & my best fashion season ever!  Plus, I love the concept of sustainable fashion.  I don't see the point of owning an extensive wardrobe when you can "borrow" whenever you need.  Plus, the level of professionalism is exceptional!  Love, Candace

originalText.text: I had such an incredible experience renting from StyeLend! As a blogger, it was amazing to be able to rent a gorgeous dress that I normally wouldn't be able to afford. The fit was absolutely amazing. Lona and the rest of the team were such a pleasure to work with, and I will definitely be renting again in the future!! This is such a sustainable and innovative company, and I'm so happy I found out about it☺️ Renting was extremely easy and hassle free, and my item was in perfect condition.

originalText.text: I didn't realize how much a dress can make you feel like a million bucks until I rented one from StyleLend.   It was for a trip to New York.  I wore the dress to go to a couple of events and when I walked around the city the complements and  head turns were a complete self esteem makeover!  I have another rental coming in the mail and can't wait!  This is much more fun than buying a dress and having it sit in a closet. Thanks!
